    <title>Week3-8937</title>
    <link href="/2025/10/31/Week3-8937/"/>
    <url>/2025/10/31/Week3-8937/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="前置知识前缀和">前置知识：前缀和</h1><h2 id="基础认识">基础认识:</h2><ul><li><p>前缀和是什么</p><p>可以简单理解为 数列的前 𝑛 项的和</p></li><li><p>前缀和有什么用</p><p>用于快速求解区间和</p></li><li><p>前缀和的地位</p><p>是一种重要的预处理思想</p></li></ul><h2 id="一维前缀和">一维前缀和</h2><p>对于长度为 <span class="math inline"><em>n</em></span> 的数列 {<spanclass="math inline"><em>a</em><sub><em>i</em></sub></span>},如果要多次查询区间 <spanclass="math inline">[<em>l</em>, <em>r</em>]</span>的所有数字之和，就可以考虑使用前缀和。</p><h3 id="递推式">递推式</h3><p><span class="math inline"><em>s</em><sub>0</sub> = 0</span></p><p><spanclass="math inline"><em>s</em><sub><em>i</em></sub> = <em>s</em><sub><em>i</em> − 1</sub> + <em>a</em><sub><em>i</em></sub></span></p><p>是不是很像高中学的数列前 <span class="math inline"><em>n</em></span>项和 <spanclass="math inline"><em>s</em><sub><em>n</em></sub></span></p><h3 id="查询">查询</h3><p>现在假设我们需要查询 <spanclass="math inline">[<em>l</em>, <em>r</em>]</span>之间数的和，就可以使用公式 <spanclass="math inline"><em>s</em><sub><em>r</em></sub> − <em>s</em><sub><em>l</em> − 1</sub></span>来计算区间和。</p><h3 id="对比">对比</h3><p>因此，我们便可以在 <span class="math inline"><em>O</em>(1)</span>的时间查询到区间 <spanclass="math inline">[<em>l</em>, <em>r</em>]</span> 的和，代价是我们需要<span class="math inline"><em>O</em>(<em>n</em>)</span>的时间进行计算所有 <span class="math inline"><em>n</em></span>的前缀和。</p><p>示例：对于 <span class="math inline"><em>m</em></span> 个查询区间<span class="math inline">[<em>l</em>, <em>r</em>]</span>。如果采用暴力算法，对每个区间进行遍历求和，时间复杂度为 <spanclass="math inline"><em>O</em>(<em>m</em> * <em>n</em>)</span></p><p>但是用前缀和优化查询，时间复杂度为 <spanclass="math inline"><em>O</em>(<em>n</em> + <em>m</em>)</span></p><p>这么对比能大概 get 到前缀和的用途了吗？</p><blockquote><p>这里看不懂 <span class="math inline"><em>O</em>(...)</span>是什么可以留个概念，有这么个玩意，等之后老师讲，或者直接问学长。</p></blockquote><h1 id="具体思路">具体思路</h1><p>上面解释了前缀和的基础知识。相信你已经对这道题有了一定的思路了。</p><p>假如你因为不了解前缀和而写不出来，可以暂停阅读，想一想前缀和应该怎么应用到这道题上。</p><p>如果还是没什么思路，就跟着我下面的来看看这道题。</p><h2 id="题意分析">题意分析</h2><p>题目要求一个数列被分成两半后，左右两边和的差值的最小值。</p><p>注意到要求和</p><h2 id="最直观的想法暴力">最直观的想法，暴力</h2><p>简单来说，我们可以假设每两个数之间被切一刀，然后数组被分成两半，然后我们计算两边的和的差值，更新最小值即可。</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; ++ i ) <br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> left = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, right = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> j = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; j &lt;= i; ++ j ) &#123;<br>        left += a[i];<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> j = i<span class="hljs-number">+1</span>; j &lt;= n; ++ j ) &#123;<br>        right += a[i];<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> diff = <span class="hljs-built_in">abs</span>( left - right );<br>    ans = <span class="hljs-built_in">min</span>( ans, diff );<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>但是这种写法无疑会暴力运算每一个区间，最终的时间复杂度为 <spanclass="math inline"><em>O</em>(<em>n</em><sup>2</sup>)</span>。</p><p>对于这题 <span class="math inline"><em>n</em> ≤ 1<em>e</em>5</span>来说，最终时间为 <span class="math inline">1<em>e</em>10</span> 超过了<span class="math inline">1<em>s</em></span> 时间限制的 <spanclass="math inline">1<em>e</em>8</span> 的数据处理量。</p><blockquote><p><span class="math inline">1<em>e</em>5 = 10<sup>5</sup></span>科学技术法 方便书写</p><p>一般来说，计算机 <span class="math inline">1<em>s</em></span> 能执行<span class="math inline">1<em>e</em>8</span> 的数据处理。</p><p>所以对于输入数据的规模，我们需要找到不同时间复杂度的算法来解决问题。</p><p>这就是算法的应用，你理解了吗？</p></blockquote><p>因此，我们需要一个更加优秀的算法解决这个问题。</p><h2 id="不难想到的优化前缀和">不难想到的优化，前缀和</h2><p>根据之前对题目的分析，我们发现，其实我们每次对 <spanclass="math inline">[1, <em>j</em>]</span> 以及 <spanclass="math inline">[<em>j</em> + 1, <em>n</em>]</span>两个区间的求和占据了很多时间，而这种区间求和，我们则可以使用前缀和来优化。</p><p>不难想到</p><p>区间 <span class="math inline">[1, <em>j</em>]</span> 的和即 <spanclass="math inline"><em>s</em><sub><em>j</em></sub> − <em>s</em><sub>0</sub></span></p><p>区间 <span class="math inline">[<em>j</em> + 1, <em>n</em>]</span>的和即 <spanclass="math inline"><em>s</em><sub><em>n</em></sub> − <em>s</em><sub><em>j</em></sub></span></p><p>所以如果我们对每个位置进行判断该不该切一刀，每次只需要用两个算式计算两边大小就行，不用每个求和过去，</p><p>这样的话，时间复杂度就是 <spanclass="math inline"><em>O</em>(<em>n</em> * 2)</span>。</p><p>因为复杂度可以消去常数，所以理论上就是 <spanclass="math inline"><em>O</em>(<em>n</em>)</span>。</p><p>对于这道 <span class="math inline">1<em>e</em>5</span> 的 <spanclass="math inline"><em>n</em></span> ，完全足以胜任。</p><p>以下是代码实现</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; ++ +i ) &#123;<br>    sum[i] = sum[i<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>] + a[i];<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> ans = <span class="hljs-number">1e9</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; ++ i ) &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> left = sum[i] - sum[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>];<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> right = sum[n] - sum[i];<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> diff = <span class="hljs-built_in">abs</span>( left - right );<br>    ans = <span class="hljs-built_in">min</span>( ans, diff );  <br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="不过这题还没结束">不过这题还没结束</h3><p>还有一个隐藏陷阱，注意到 <spanclass="math inline"><em>a</em> ≤ 1<em>e</em>5</span>，并且<spanclass="math inline"><em>n</em> ≤ 1<em>e</em>5</span>。</p><p>所以，极端情况下，我们会处理到的区间和最大为 <spanclass="math inline"><em>n</em> * <em>a</em></span>，大小为<spanclass="math inline">1<em>e</em>5 * 1<em>e</em>5 = 1<em>e</em>10</span>。</p><p>而我们的 <spanclass="math inline"><em>i</em><em>n</em><em>t</em></span> 整数类型只能存<span class="math inline">2<sup>31</sup> − 1</span> 也就是差不多 <spanclass="math inline">1<em>e</em>9</span> 的数字。</p><p>所以，我们还需要使用 <spanclass="math inline"><em>l</em><em>o</em><em>n</em><em>g</em><em>l</em><em>o</em><em>n</em><em>g</em></span>来存储数据。</p><p>最后给出ac代码</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">namespace</span> std;<br><span class="hljs-comment">// 上面的头文件不用管，c++写法</span><br><br><span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> maxn = <span class="hljs-number">1e5</span> + <span class="hljs-number">50</span>;<br><span class="hljs-comment">// 此处表示定义maxn为一个常量</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 常量即一个不可修改的值</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 所以是静态的数据，可以用来定义数组大小</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 还有一个注意点，因为数组是从0开始计数的</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 所以如果刚刚好开 1e5 的大小，第 1e5 个数字会无法访问到。</span><br><br><span class="hljs-type">long</span> <span class="hljs-type">long</span> a[maxn];<br><span class="hljs-type">long</span> <span class="hljs-type">long</span> sum[maxn];<br><span class="hljs-comment">// 这里用maxn定义大小方便</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 如果每次修改大小，只需要修改上面的值</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 不用对每一个数组大小进行修改</span><br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> n;<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d&quot;</span>, &amp;n);<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 输入</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; ++ i ) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d&quot;</span>, &amp;a[i]);<br>        sum[i] = sum[i<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>] + a[i];<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 初始化</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-type">long</span> <span class="hljs-type">long</span> ans = <span class="hljs-number">1e18</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; ++ i ) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">long</span> <span class="hljs-type">long</span> left = sum[i];<br>        <span class="hljs-type">long</span> <span class="hljs-type">long</span> right = sum[n] - sum[i];<br>        ans = <span class="hljs-built_in">min</span>( ans, <span class="hljs-built_in">abs</span>( left - right ) );<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 数据处理</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%lld\n&quot;</span>, ans);<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 输出部分</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>很感谢你能看到这里，愿你在 ac过程中不断成长，每一次提交都能学到一点新东西。</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
